org.eclipse.eef

Interface EEFDynamicMappingFor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    EEFControlDescription, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EEFDynamicMappingForImpl

    public interface EEFDynamicMappingFor
extends EEFControlDescription
    A representation of the model object 'EEF Dynamic Mapping For'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Iterator
    • Iterable Expression
    • Force Refresh
    • Ifs
    See Also:
    EefPackage.getEEFDynamicMappingFor()
